KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_ARBITRARY_ENZYME_REACTIONS

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_ARBITRARY_ENZYME_REACTIONS
Determines the key for the standard kinetic law to be applied for reactions that are identified to be enzyme-catalyzed (with or without explicit catalyst) and that do not belong to one of the other standard enzyme-catalysis schemes. The value can be any rate law that implements InterfaceArbitraryEnzymeKinetics.

KINETICS_GENE_REGULATION

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_GENE_REGULATION
Determines the key for the standard kinetic law to be applied for reactions that are identified to belong to gene-regulatory processes, such as transcription or translation. The value is the class name of any class that implements the org.sbml.squeezer.kinetics.InterfaceGeneRegulatoryNetworks.

KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_NON_ENZYME_REACTIONS

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_NON_ENZYME_REACTIONS
Determines the key for the standard kinetic law to be applied for reactions that are catalyzed by non-enzymes or that are not catalyzed at all. The value may be any rate law that implements InterfaceNonEnzymeKinetics.

KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_NON_ENZYME_REACTIONS

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_NON_ENZYME_REACTIONS
Determines the key for the standard kinetic law to be applied for reactions that are catalyzed by non-enzymes or that are not catalyzed at all. The value may be any rate law that implements InterfaceNonEnzymeKinetics.

KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_UNI_UNI_TYPE

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_UNI_UNI_TYPE
This key defines the default kinetic law to be applied to enzyme-catalyzed reactions with one reactant and one product. Possible values are the names of classes that implement InterfaceUniUniKinetics.

KINETICS_ZERO_REACTANTS

KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_BI_BI_TYPE

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_BI_BI_TYPE
The class name of the default kinetic law for reversible bi-bi reactions. This can be any class that implements the InterfaceBiBiKinetics and InterfaceReversibleKinetics.

KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_BI_BI_TYPE

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_BI_BI_TYPE
The class name of the default kinetic law for irreversible bi-bi reactions. This can be any class that implements the InterfaceBiBiKinetics and InterfaceIrreversibleKinetics.

KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_BI_UNI_TYPE

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_REVERSIBLE_BI_UNI_TYPE
The class name of the default kinetic law for bi-uni reactions. This can be any class that implements the InterfaceBiUniKinetics.

KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_BI_UNI_TYPE

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_BI_UNI_TYPE
The class name of the default kinetic law for bi-uni reactions. This can be any class that implements the InterfaceBiUniKinetics.

KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_UNI_UNI_TYPE

static final de.zbit.util.prefs.Option<Class> KINETICS_IRREVERSIBLE_UNI_UNI_TYPE
This key defines the default kinetic law to be applied to enzyme-catalyzed reactions with one reactant and one product. Possible values are the names of classes that implement InterfaceUniUniKinetics.
